  "tan(theta) = h/2000. sec^2(theta) * dtheta/dt = (1/2000) * dh/dt. When h = 1500: tan(theta) = 3/4, sec^2(theta) = 1 + 9/16 = 25/16. (25/16) * dtheta/dt = 600/2000 = 0.3. dtheta/dt = 0.3 * 16/25 = 4.8/25 = 0.192 rad/s.": "",
